---
name: File Naming Conventions
description: Maintain consistent file naming for React components and utilities.
tags: [naming, conventions, components]
---

- Use **CamcelCase** for React components (e.g., `MapSidebar.tsx`).
- Use **camelCase** for utility and logic files (e.g., `getDefaultCursor.ts`).
- Use **kebab-case** for SCSS/CSS files if used (e.g., `map-sidebar.module.scss`).
- Use WordPress coding standards and filenaming standards to name files in PSR-4 format (/Admin/Admin_Components.php)
- Use WordPress JavaScript standards for filenames.
